      "explanation": “Master bakers possess decades of accumulated experience, allowing them to intuitively adjust processes based on subtle observations – the feel of the dough, the aroma, the appearance of the crust. Capturing and replicating this ‘tacit knowledge’ in an automated system is incredibly difficult. While machine learning can be used to analyze data, it’s unlikely to fully understand or compensate for the nuanced judgments of a skilled artisan.

